ictim<br />\n<br />\n冤冤相報何時了<br />\n依家雙方嘅理性球迷都知<br />\n唔應該嘲諷災難<br />\n奈何永遠都有老鼠屎搞事"},{"pid":"aee47ff82eda01171d4d803b39673882fd8e4255","tid":1916374,"uid":75028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1db3d696b99d391cbc2e445c700fabdf149a4688","tid":1916374,"uid":13504,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:08:44.000Z","msg":"香港本土來講<br />\n肯定係獌迷質素問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而依個問題到依家都一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全解釋點解曼聯廢咗咁多都仲咁多人反獌"},{"pid":"ebb816d50bc684b427822566039bada7c899590f","tid":1916374,"uid":75028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"英國足球文化係咁<br />\n憎到死敵入骨<br />\n<br />\n修咸頓樸茨茅夫唔同組別咁多年都好憎對方<br />\n韋斯咸 米禾爾對親都暴動咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0028cfdd214c57183f11042191759d393eb2fd42","tid":1916374,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b8bd3d80ee07b79ef501d26f7fab832d6a81b34","tid":1916374,"uid":8636,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"曼係原罪嘛<br />\n講咁多做咩<br />\n自己串咀就無問題，因為咩都係曼迷串咀先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:05:59.000Z","msg":"曼聯就黑哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他就誤判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55cec49949d912fa13800d7caf037a48539eb98","tid":1916374,"uid":67225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1db3d696b99d391cbc2e445c700fabdf149a4688","tid":1916374,"uid":13504,"like":11,"dislike":